blogs.title: Getting Started with React
blogs.description: Learn the basics of React and how to build modern web applications
blogs.content:
React is a powerful JavaScript library for building user interfaces. In this blog, we'll explore the fundamental concepts of React including components, state management, and hooks. React makes it easy to create interactive UIs by breaking them down into reusable components.

One of the key benefits of React is its virtual DOM, which makes rendering efficient. When state changes, React updates only the necessary parts of the DOM, resulting in better performance.
